Perlbug README

Short instructions:

    unpack Perlbug_2.26.tar.gz
    
    cd ./Perlbug_2.26
    
	modify ./config/Configuration
	
    perl Makefile.PL PREFIX=Perlbug_installation

    make 
 
    make test
    
    make install
    

Long instructions:

    See INSTALL and 'perldoc Perlbug'
 
	More docs under construction

